      <h1>Joao V. Rocha.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Decade behind the desk. A1 in São Paulo, A2 at Rock in Rio, now AV at
        Sound Image / Clair Global for clients like Apple and Dolby. Builds
        the software and hardware the operations floor is missing.
      </p>
    </header>
